_278_orchid_1#2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "还有泡普卡——", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "char_278_orchid_1#2"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_282_catap_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "梓兰姐，你的意思是，这一切都是个骗局？", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_282_catap_1#7$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "char_278_orchid_1#1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "还记得我们之前在萨尔贡吧？", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "char_278_orchid_1#1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萨尔贡的某些帕夏，常会因为太过无聊而在自己的领地中做一些匪夷所思的事，比如说，这里也有可能是一座处在绿洲中的巨大摄影棚。", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "char_278_orchid_1#1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_282_catap_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "空爆", "content": "哇哦，我也想体验这种有钱人的生活——"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_282_catap_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "空爆", "content": "呃，不对，要是这么说的话，我现在已经在体验了。"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_282_catap_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但那三个人又要怎么解释呢？", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_282_catap_1#11$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "char_278_orchid_1#1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "帕夏的手下往往有许多能人异士，或许他们的认知被修改了。", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "char_278_orchid_1#1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_282_catap_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "为啥是他们？", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_282_catap_1#11$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "char_278_orchid_1#2", "focus": "r"}}, {"